# ComplaintManagementSystem
Online Complaint Management System provides a digitalized way of resolving the problems faced by the public by saving time and to some extent eradicate corruption. 
The objective of the Complaint Management System is to provide an easier way to file Complaints by the user and for police officials, it makes complaints easier to coordinate, monitor, track and resolve issues. 
The user files their complaint by providing their Aadhar Number and E-mail ID. The complaints filed will be confidential. 
Online Complaint Management is a management technique for assessing, analyzing and responding to customer complaints. The proposed system is used to record , resolve and respond to customer complaints, requests as well as facilitate any other feedback. 
This system will help the user to save time and also the user will know the status of the complaints without going to the police station often.
